<paragraph id="8BEF36A3FFD1FFF0A5F8F96B1D88F8F8" blockId="33.[136,1452,1029,1884]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD1FFF0A5F8F96B1F19F90C" bold="true" box="[189,294,1714,1740]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C504D20FFD1FFF0A463F9681FE1F90B" authorityName="Kunth" authorityYear="1817" box="[294,478,1713,1739]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" genus="Verbena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="litoralis">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD1FFF0A463F9681FE1F90B" box="[294,478,1713,1739]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Verbena litoralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a herbaceous species presenting glabrescent branches; membranaceous leaves; strigose calyx, and corolla slightly exceeding the calyx. It can be differentiated from 
<taxonomicName id="4C504D20FFD1FFF0A6B9F90F1A61F92F" authorityName="Sprengel" authorityYear="1827" box="[1020,1118,1749,1775]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" genus="Verbena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rigida">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD1FFF0A6B9F90F1A61F92F" box="[1020,1118,1749,1775]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">V. rigida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the branches glabrescent, bracts shorter than the calyx, and corolla minute up to 
<quantity id="4CA89B46FFD1FFF0A7B3F9231D07F8D4" box="[758,824,1786,1812]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" unit="mm" value="4.0">4 mm</quantity>
long (
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD1FFF0A6C1F9231D9DF8D3" box="[900,930,1786,1811]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">vs.</emphasis>
hispid branches; bracts longer than the calyx, and corolla approximately three times longer than the calyx in 
<taxonomicName id="4C504D20FFD1FFF0A602F8C71D99F8F7" authorityName="Sprengel" authorityYear="1827" box="[839,934,1821,1847]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" genus="Verbena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rigida">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD1FFF0A602F8C71D99F8F7" box="[839,934,1821,1847]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">V. rigida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
